VALUATION
For finding the 'best' position for the hero based on a given state:
  Given a set of rain objects, find the x coordinate within screen bounds that
    maximizes horizontal distance from closest raindrops left+right OR
    manhattan distance from hero center if there is no posn which has 0 rain overhead

INPUTS

(hero_posn, hero_speed,  [rain], optimal_posn, optimal_direction)

OUTPUT
(direction)
